channel.title: Blog
channel.description: Cute pictures and captions of my life in New Mexico. This is my blog and I post what makes me happy. I hope you like it.

item.title: Father’s Day
item.description: My boys are so lucky to have Jared (My husband, lover, friend, etc) as their dad. He is totally amazing and I really don’t have words to describe what a wonderful man he is.
